snippet.title: Sedap! A Culinary Adventure - Official Release Date Trailer | The MIX Fall Showcase 2024
snippet.description: SEDAP! is a co-op cooking adventure that combines the chaos of a collaborative kitchen and the wonders of adventuring into an unexplored world. Embark on an exciting culinary journey, whip up delectable delicacies, and serve your way through a fantastical reimagination of Southeast Asia! Watch the Sedap! trailer to see cooking gameplay and the colorful world of this co-op cooking adventure game. Sedap! A Culinary Adventure will be available on PC, Nintendo Switch, Xbox, and PlayStation on March 13, 2025, and a demo is out now on Steam.
